{
  "name": "Spike Growth",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The ground in a 20-foot-radius Sphere centered on a point within range sprouts hard spikes and thorns. The area becomes Difficult Terrain for the duration. When a creature moves into or within the area, it takes [[/damage 2d4 type=piercing]] damage for every 5 feet it travels.</p><p>The transformation of the ground is camouflaged to look natural. Any creature that can't see the area when the spell is cast must take a Search action and succeed on a [[/check ability=wis skill=prc dc=@attributes.spelldc]] or [[/check ability=wis skill=sur dc=@attributes.spelldc]] check against your spell save DC to recognize the terrain as hazardous before entering it.</p>",
